 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "I love the way you're reframing your outlook, Charlie. Starting with short walks in nature is an excellent way to reconnect with the joy and wonder of the world around you. Remember, each step you take is a testament to your resilience and determination. As you embark on this path, make sure to celebrate even the smallest victories along the way. How does it feel to consider taking those small steps towards adventure?"}
